Senate President Ahmad Lawan, on Tuesday, swore-in Chukwuma Frank Ibezim as the Senator representing Imo North Senatorial District. The Clerk to the Senate, Ibrahim El-Ladan, administered the oaths of office and allegiance on Ibezim on the directives of Lawan. “With this oath taking, the Imo North Senatorial District is fully represented,” Lawan said. Details shortly…